## ✨ What's New

### 🤖 **9 Specialized AI Agents**
- **full-stack-developer**: Complete web application development
- **devops-infrastructure**: Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD pipelines
- **testing-stability-expert**: Comprehensive testing and validation
- **performance-optimizer**: Performance profiling and optimization
- **code-reviewer**: Security and quality code reviews
- **docs-master**: Documentation creation and verification
- **repo-optimizer**: Repository setup and tooling

### 🔧 **18 MCP Servers**
**Core**: filesystem, git, github, python-analysis, memory, sequential-thinking  
**Data**: sqlite, postgres  
**Web**: puppeteer, fetch, brave-search  
**Infrastructure**: docker, kubernetes  
**Communication**: slack, time  
**Cloud**: aws, sentry, gitlab

### 🎨 **Enhanced Web GUI**
- **Multi-tab Interface**: Chat, Code Editor, Terminal
- **Agent Selector**: Switch between AI agents on the fly
- **Code Editor**: Syntax highlighting with CodeMirror
- **Live Terminal**: Interactive command execution
- **Real-time Stats**: Monitor workspace performance
- **Dynamic Backend Detection**: Automatically finds backend on any port
- **Remote Access Support**: Works seamlessly on VPS deployments

